
server side

required node modules
- node-gyp 
- node-ursa -( requires openSSL)
- node-aes-256-gcm 

usage :   var encrypted_message = encodeCipher(clientPublicKey, 'Message to encrypt'));
 

client side usage

	Crypto crypto = new Crypto(context);

for first time - registration
        String publicKey = crypto.getPublicKey());
	
for decoding encomming message
String x = crypto.decodeCipher(encrypted_message)





  
